title: Ofra Haza (1995) The Golden Album 2CD 320k (musicfromrizzo)
description:
This is the nicest CD set offering Ive heard from Israel - done by the late dear Ofra Haza whose life was taken prematurely as a result if AIDS contracted it is believed from her unfaithful husband.

It includes the song Galbi - a big hit for a time on particular New York radio stations - however it was necessary in my view to include as a bonus the
song as Ofra Haza originally performed it rather than the almost unrecognizable
unneccesary variation on this CD I believe.

There's even a song in French. A lot of the beat on this album sounds like music
meant to inspire modern day dance as an alternative to older styles of expression
I believe.

enjoy the CD set and please seed this one too if you are a fan
of world music and wish to see it promote your culture perhaps too

with thanks

Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
